{"id": 2367, "genre": 1001, "title": "出门在外，你在「不想和人接触」上都使过哪些劲？", "description": "一个自诊「社恐病患」的自我修养。（题图来自：istock © dan4）", "record_count": 4014, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180523113926PsJCf9evSo5Lmkri.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-06-22T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 288768, "content": "只看除了人以外的东西 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380658}, {"id": 289024, "content": "长辈恐惧症", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1382794}, {"id": 288769, "content": "耍手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1096161}, {"id": 289025, "content": "害怕考试", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1382794}, {"id": 289026, "content": "碰见熟悉的人想打招呼，但不知道说什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1382794}, {"id": 289028, "content": "是否有什么办法呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1104200}, {"id": 289540, "content": "把自己当哑巴，出门逛街买东西用手指指和点头摇头，可以不对人说一句话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1382902}, {"id": 290565, "content": "为了不要坐一班地铁，躲在厕所等下一班", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390404}, {"id": 288774, "content": "戴口罩！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380677}, {"id": 289030, "content": "聚会时，不管有没人找，总是假装在认真看手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1382828}, {"id": 288775, "content": "麦当劳的自助点餐器", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297298}, {"id": 289031, "content": "手机全年静音", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1382852}, {"id": 288776, "content": "Leave me alone", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 316103}, {"id": 289544, "content": "即使不听音乐，我也要带上耳机，你们说什么？我听不见", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1234107}, {"id": 288777, "content": "假装很忙", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380688}, {"id": 289033, "content": "有半熟不熟的人微信联系我或者打电话时，装作没看见，过一个小时再回", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1382064}, {"id": 289289, "content": "走一半思考人生；热得出汗了思考人生，不出汗了再走；吃一半思考人生； \r\n实测，再也没人随便约我出去。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379658}, {"id": 288778, "content": "尽量不抬头 带耳机听歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380692}, {"id": 288779, "content": "不戴眼镜出门", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1358445}, {"id": 290315, "content": "眼神跳跃式转向远方", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016340}, {"id": 288780, "content": "座位靠窗，习惯性望窗外", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380695}, {"id": 289037, "content": "喜欢一个人在家里独处的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1363393}, {"id": 289039, "content": "不想打招呼了，低头装作玩手机没看到", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094614}, {"id": 288784, "content": "你先把目光落到他身上你就输了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380704}, {"id": 288785, "content": "即使麦当劳没人排队也喜欢用自助点单机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346901}, {"id": 289041, "content": "听音乐\n看视频\n玩手游", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1382441}, {"id": 288786, "content": "大老远地看见熟人，看到他装作没看见我，于是我也装作看不见他了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1305504}, {"id": 288787, "content": "不回话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 748704}, {"id": 288788, "content": "让他自己感到无趣", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380730}, {"id": 288789, "content": "强迫自己不断唱歌点歌上厕所", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1351762}, {"id": 288790, "content": "刷起自己以前不怎么刷的微博", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1351762}, {"id": 288791, "content": "不戴眼镜，宁愿不看请这个世界，才觉得世界只属于自己一个人，很享受\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379744}, {"id": 289048, "content": "行走或排队会和人保持一公尺距离 如果有人因为贴太近碰到我 会很反感", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1294407}, {"id": 289049, "content": "不去那种店主很自来熟的小卖部。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 133780}, {"id": 288794, "content": "低头玩儿手机，或者转移目光，假装没看到", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380753}, {"id": 288795, "content": "直接无视", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1332329}, {"id": 288796, "content": "见面微笑一下，点点头，然后转移视线，不发一语。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 545614}, {"id": 289052, "content": "呆在家了，看动漫，看电影，随便找点事干", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1383111}, {"id": 289056, "content": "哪里人少去哪里  不喜欢被人关注 走路戴耳机不放音乐  远距离看都熟人绕路  离得近随机应变  好朋友会打招呼  ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1273401}, {"id": 288802, "content": "能自己搞懂的决不问别人", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380766}, {"id": 288805, "content": "放假在家跟朋友约好什么时候出去\n但是到那天又给自己找理由能不能不去", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380768}, {"id": 288806, "content": "好友微信群响个不停不想回复，想发点什么害怕被人发现自己上微信忍着不发", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380769}, {"id": 288811, "content": "走小道，寻幽处，乐在其中！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380363}, {"id": 288812, "content": "不带耳机不出门星人", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1250694}, {"id": 289328, "content": "能发微信就绝不打电话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1384334}, {"id": 288817, "content": "一个人走路也要假装看着手机，打着电话，怕自己不知道眼神看哪，孤单和无助；怕别人觉得自己很奇怪；让别人觉得自己很忙，有事做！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380793}, {"id": 288819, "content": "你好", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380806}, {"id": 288821, "content": "不出门儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380815}, {"id": 288823, "content": "看到电梯人多就去走楼梯", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118083}, {"id": 288824, "content": "上出租或者滴滴的第一件事就是和司机说师傅我带耳机了，如果您之后说话我没能及时回复很抱歉 这样师傅就不会找你闲聊了。第一对他人是种尊重，第二也适合像我这样有点社交恐惧的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380857}]}